@page "/"

<div class="hero-section" data-aos="fade-down">
    <div class="hero-text">
        <h1>Escape to Your Private Paradise</h1>
        <p>Discover the perfect vacation rental for relaxation and adventure in Ho Chi Minh City.</p>
        <a class="cta-button" href="/locations">Check Availability</a>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="content-section">
    <div class="section property-highlights" data-aos="fade-up">
        <div class="hero-text">
            <h2>Why Stay Here?</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Rich History and Culture</li>
                <li>Delicious Food</li>
                <li>Vibrant Nightlife</li>
                <li>Warm Climate</li>
                <li>Fully-equipped kitchen, Wi-Fi, and Smart TV</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section guest-testimonials" data-aos="fade-left">
        <div class="hero-text">
            <h2>What Our Guests Say</h2>
            <div class="testimonial">
                <p>"The perfect getaway! The view was incredible, and the house had everything we needed. We'll be back for sure!"</p>
                <span>- Sarah J.</span>
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial">
                <p>"A fantastic vacation spot! The pool and outdoor area made for a relaxing stay. Highly recommend this place."</p>
                <span>- Mark T.</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section local-attractions" data-aos="fade-right">
        <div class="hero-text">
            <h2>Explore the Area</h2>
            <p>Our vacation rental is located just minutes away from some of the top attractions in the area:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Ben Thanh Market</li>
                <li>Scenic Independence Palace</li>
                <li>Local restaurants, cafes, and boutique shops</li>
                <li>Wineries and cultural landmarks</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Check out all that Ho Chi Minh City has to offer!</p>
            <div class="booking-section">
                <a class="cta-button" href="/locations">Check Availability</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

